co-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pvd1665702680030.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pvd1665702680030.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pvd1665702680030.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pvd1665702680030\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the email address that is to receive any replies to the current\n    message.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__topic_d134684e1_d134685e1_d134686e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__p_d134687e1_d134688e1_d134689e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SetReplyTo</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">ReplyTo</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__section_dfh_dtb_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d829767e65\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__table_w5375ab1b5b3b3_w5376ab1b5b3_w5377ab1b5_w5378ab1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__table_w5375ab1b5b3b3_w5376ab1b5b3_w5377ab1b5_w5378ab1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__table_w5375ab1b5b3b3_w5376ab1b5b3_w5377ab1b5_w5378ab1__entry__2\">Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__table_w5375ab1b5b3b3_w5376ab1b5b3_w5377ab1b5_w5378ab1__entry__3\">Direction</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__table_w5375ab1b5b3b3_w5376ab1b5b3_w5377ab1b5_w5378ab1__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pvd1665702680030__table_w5375ab1b5b3b3_w5376ab1b5b3_w5377ab1b5_w5378ab1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ReplyTo</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pvd1665702680030__table_w5375ab1b5b3b3_w5376ab1b5b3_w5377ab1b5_w5378ab1__entry__2\">string</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pvd1665702680030__table_w5375ab1b5b3b3_w5376ab1b5b3_w5377ab1b5_w5378ab1__entry__3\">In</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pvd1665702680030__table_w5375ab1b5b3b3_w5376ab1b5b3_w5377ab1b5_w5378ab1__entry__4\">Email address to receive any replies; maximum of 1024\n          bytes</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__section_xvg_2tb_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d829767e125\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in $status</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pvd1665702680030__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pvd1665702680030__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">Operation succeeded</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pvd1665702680030__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">-18</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pvd1665702680030__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">Memory allocation error</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pvd1665702680030__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__1\">&lt;0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pvd1665702680030__table_d16103e1_d16104e1_d16105e1__entry__2\">An error occurred</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__section_opm_gtb_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d829767e186\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">You can use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SetReplyTo</span> operation to specify an email address to\n        receive replies. For example, if you have sent an information message that is not intended\n        to get replies, you can set the <code class=\"ph codeph\">ReplyTo</code> email address to a another account\n        that generates an automatic message.</p>\n</section>\n<div class=\"example\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__example_fcg_htb_gwb\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"pvd1665702680030__pre_gcg_htb_gwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">mailApiHandle-&gt;ReplyTo(\"noreply@mygreatcorp.com\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531094\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531094\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "SetReplyTo Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify the email address that is to receive any replies to the current message. SetReplyTo ( ReplyTo ) Parameters Parameter Type Direction Description ReplyTo string In Email address to receive any replies; maximum of 1024 bytes Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $status Value Description 0 Operation succeeded -18 Memory allocation error <0 An error occurred Description You can use the SetReplyTo operation to specify an email address to receive replies. For example, if you have sent an information message that is not intended to get replies, you can set the ReplyTo email address to a another account that generates an automatic message. mailApiHandle->ReplyTo(\"noreply@mygreatcorp.com\") Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}